deling by allowing continuum and atomistic $k\\cdot p$ models to\nbe combined in the same system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 1 Mar 2015 05:22:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2015 19:47:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Nov 2015 19:53:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-20"}
